Key Match Events: Zambia was reduced to 10 men after a red card to their captain Roderick Kabwe in the 44th minute
Patson Daka scored a late header to equalize the match with two minutes left on the clock
Post-Match Reflections: Patson Daka was named Man of the Match for his crucial goal
Miscellaneous Highlights: Group F remains wide open with Morocco leading on four points, followed by Democratic Republic of Congo and Zambia with two points each, and Tanzania with one point
